<br>
the second step requires 10 kromriff heads<br>
<br>
the third step requires making a tundrabear sandwich, snow bunny stew, ulthork pie, and snow griff soufle<br>
<br>
and the 4th step requires making the vial of velium vapours.<br>
<br>
<br>
here's what you need to do the whole quest so far:<br>
<br>
4 frost giant toes (off of any giant in velious)<br>
10 kromriff heads  (off of any giant in velious)<br>
1 tundra kodiak meat (off of tundra kodiaks in EW)<br>
2 snow bunny meats  (off of snow bunnies in EW)<br>
2 ulthork meats  (off of any ulthork in EW)<br>
4 snow griffin eggs (off of snow griffs in EW)<br>
1 pot<br>
1 pie tin<br>
2 jug o'sauces<br>
1 loaf of bread<br>
1 mixing bowl<br>
3 spices<br>
2 flasks of water<br>
1 vinegar<br>
1 clump of dough (1 egg, 1 flour, 1 milk)<br>
3 crystalline spider silks<br>
2 small pieces of velium<br>
2 glass shards<br>
1 High Quality firing sheet<br>
1 small brick of velium<br>
<br>
<br>
that's your grocery list of everything you need.  this is all you need unless you fail on making something.  when turning in your 3rd shawl and seal, make sure it's to borannin and not the historian.<br>
